{
  "text": "Literature retrieval and selection criteria A literature retrieval was performed covering the Cochrane library, PubMed, Web of Science, Embase, and Ovid for articles that met the following search strategies: [CITATION_1] Frey . In addition, references from retrieved articles were screened to identify possibly missed studies by literature retrieval. All identified studies were screened and judged whether they were eligible for inclusion criteria by two authors independently.",
